msgstr "Oh, parece que me han solicitado."

msgctxt "1428_Erena"
msgid "Enjoy your stay, okay?"
msgstr "Disfruta de tu estancia, ¿sí?"

msgctxt "1440_Erena"
msgid "Bye for now."
msgstr "Hasta luego."

msgctxt "1452_Erena"
msgid "Hi. I'm Erena. Nice to meet you."
msgstr "Soy Erena. Un gusto en conocerte."

msgctxt "1464_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm Kazuma Kiryu. Likewise."
msgstr "Soy Kazuma Kiryu. El gusto es todo mío."

msgctxt "1476_Erena"
msgid "Ooh, you're such a manly man, Kiryu-san. You're really my type."
msgstr "Ooh, eres muy masculino, Kiryu-san. Realmente eres mi tipo."

msgctxt "1488_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. You don't say?"
msgstr "¿Realmente lo crees?"

msgctxt "1500_Erena"
msgid "I love men who act big and strong, but get gentle when they're alone with a woman."
msgstr "Amo a los hombres que actúan ser grandes y fuertes, pero que son gentiles cuando están a solas con una mujer."

msgctxt "1512_Kiryu"
msgid "I don't think I'm like that..."
msgstr "No creo que sea ese tipo de persona..."

msgctxt "1524_Erena"
msgid "Really? Nobody has to act cool when they're alone with the one they love."
msgstr "¿En serio? Nadie actúa tan genial cuando está a solas con alguien que ama."

msgctxt "1536_Kiryu"
msgid "You're from the Kansai area, aren't you? How long have you been in Kamurocho?"
msgstr "Vienes de la zona de Kansai, ¿no es así? ¿Por cuánto tiempo has estado en Kamurocho?"

msgctxt "1548_Erena"
msgid "Oh, not that long. I used to live in Kyoto."
msgstr "Oh, no por mucho tiempo. Antes vivía en Kyoto."

msgctxt "1560_Kiryu"
msgid "Were you a hostess in Kyoto, too?"
msgstr "¿También fuiste una hostess en Kyoto?"

msgctxt "1572_Erena"
msgid "That's right. How'd you know that?"
msgstr "Así es. ¿Cómo lo supiste?"

msgctxt "1584_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. It's just something about you. You're so flashy. It reminded me of the hostesses I've met in Osaka."
msgstr "Je. Es solo algo sobre ti. Eres tan llamativa. E incluso me recordó a las hostesses que conocí en Osaka."

msgctxt "1596_Chihiro"
msgid "Wow. So you've been to hostess clubs in Osaka too, huh?"
msgstr "Ooh. ¿Así que también fuiste a los clubes de hostess en Osaka? ¿Eh?"

msgctxt "1608_Erena"
msgid "But we Kyoto girls are more refined, as I'm sure you can tell."
msgstr "Pero las chicas de Kyoto somos mas refinadas, estoy totalmente segura."

msgctxt "1620_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh..."
msgstr "Je..."

msgctxt "1632_Erena"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Do you like this club?"
msgstr "Kiryu-san! Do you like this club?"

msgctxt "1644_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure. It's easy to just drop in without requesting anybody."
msgstr "Sure. It's easy to just drop in without requesting anybody."

msgctxt "1656_Erena"
msgid "Are you saying there are some clubs that even you'd be reluctant to enter?"
msgstr "Are you saying there are some clubs that even you'd be reluctant to enter?"

msgctxt "1668_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, sure. The clubs with a lot of yakuza connections are different. You can't just sit back, relax, and have a drink there."
msgstr "Well, sure. The clubs with a lot of yakuza connections are different. You can't just sit back, relax, and have a drink there."

msgctxt "1680_Erena"
msgid "I guess you're right... It must be hard for the girls working there, too."
msgstr "I guess you're right... It must be hard for the girls working there, too."

msgctxt "1692_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've entered a club more than once.\r\n"
"Please notify a programmer if this message is displayed."
msgstr "The dialogue will end after one round if you've entered a club more than once.\r\n"
"Please notify a programmer if this message is displayed."

