msgctxt "1872_Erena"
msgid "It's nice to meet ya. I'm Erena."
msgstr "Es un placer conocerlo.\n"
"Me llamo Erena. ♪\n"
"Espero que nos llevemos muy bien. ♪"

msgctxt "1884_Akiyama"
msgid "Hi. I'm Shun Akiyama."
msgstr "El placer es mío. Soy Shun Akiyama."

msgctxt "1896_Akiyama"
msgid "Are you from the Kansai region, by any chance?"
msgstr "Sé que esto es algo repentino, pero ¿de casualidad no serás de Kansai?"

msgctxt "1908_Erena"
msgid "That's right."
msgstr "Así es."

msgctxt "1920_Erena"
msgid "People here notice that right away. Is my accent really that different?"
msgstr "Las personas de por acá tienden a notarlo muy rápido. ¿De verdad tengo un acento tan marcado?"

msgctxt "1932_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, it is."
msgstr "Sí, así es."

msgctxt "1944_Erena"
msgid "Seriously? Well then, can you tell which part of Kansai I'm from?"
msgstr "¿Quéééé? Entonces, ¿puedes adivinar de qué parte de Kansai soy?"

msgctxt "1956_Akiyama"
msgid "Are you from Osaka?"
msgstr "¿Eres de Osaka?"

msgctxt "1968_Erena"
msgid "Nope! I'm from Kyoto."
msgstr "Fallaste.\n"
"La gran Erena es de Kioto. ♪"

msgctxt "1980_Akiyama"
msgid "Kyoto? Really? I never would've guessed."
msgstr "¿Kioto? ¿De verdad? Nunca lo hubiera adivinado..."

msgctxt "1992_Erena"
msgid "Why'd you think I was from Osaka?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Por qué piensa que soy de Osaka?"

msgctxt "2004_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, you just seemed like the stereotypical Osaka girl. Flashy and confident."
msgstr "Mmh, es solo que tienes una vibra bastante animada, como las chicas de Osaka. Pareces la típica habitante de Kansai."

msgctxt "2016_Erena"
msgid "That's not true! I'm a refined Kyoto beauty!"
msgstr "¡Pero te equivocas por completo!\n"
"Soy una belleza refinada de Kioto. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2028_Akiyama"
msgid "Whoa, a bit forward, are we?"
msgstr "Alguien se tiene mucho aprecio, je."

msgctxt "2040_Akiyama"
msgid "I bet you're from Kyoto."
msgstr "Apuesto a que eres de Kioto."

msgctxt "2052_Erena"
msgid "Yer right! Good guess."
msgstr "¡Le atinaste!\n"
"Qué inteligente, eh. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2064_Akiyama"
msgid "It's just something about you. Kind of relaxing somehow."
msgstr "Es que contigo el ambiente... de alguna forma se siente relajante."

msgctxt "2076_Erena"
msgid "Hahah! In Kyoto we call that \"hannari.\""
msgstr "¡Ah, je, je! ♪\n"
"En Kyoto, a eso lo llamamos \"hannari\"."

msgctxt "2088_Akiyama"
msgid "Yep, that's definitely the feeling I get when I look at you."
msgstr "Tienes toda la razón.\n"
"Ese estilo tuyo tan sutil y refinado, es deslumbrante."

msgctxt "2100_Erena"
msgid "Hehe. You're good at flatterin' girls. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Je, je, je.\n"
"Por lo visto Akiyama-san es bueno adulando chicas. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2112_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm not flattering you. I really mean it."
msgstr "No estoy tratando de adularte, lo digo en serio."

msgctxt "2124_Erena"
msgid "All right, then. I'll do my best to help ya relax today."
msgstr "Uy. ♪\n"
"Entonces deja que la refinada Erena te ayude a relajarte el día de hoy. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2136_Akiyama"
msgid "Could it be Hyogo?"
msgstr "¿Acaso eres de Hyogo?"

msgctxt "2148_Erena"
msgid "Nope! I'm from Kyoto."
msgstr "Fallaste.\n"
"La gran Erena es de Kioto. ♪"

msgctxt "2160_Akiyama"
msgid "Kyoto, huh? Now that I think about it, I can tell."
msgstr "¿Kioto, eh?\n"
"Ahora que lo mencionas tiene mucho sentido."

msgctxt "2172_Erena"
msgid "Really? You're not just sayin' that?"
msgstr "¿En serio?\n"
"¿No lo estarás diciendo solo porque yo lo dije?"

msgctxt "2184_Akiyama"
msgid "Really. There's something about you. Dignified, but also relaxed. It practically screams Kyoto."
msgstr "Te lo juro. La manera en que te muestras tan tranquila y segura de ti misma, realmente grita Kioto por todos lados."

msgctxt "2196_Erena"
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr "Je, je, je. Muchas gracias. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2208_Erena"
msgid "You got kind of a restrained personality, don't you? Not like the men in Kansai."
msgstr "Sabe, usted me parece muy genial. ♪\n"
"Es muy sofisticado y cerrado a comparación de los chicos Kansai."

msgctxt "2220_Akiyama"
msgid "Really? What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¿Por qué lo dices?"

msgctxt "2232_Erena"
msgid "Kansai men are real laid-back. They'll meet someone for the first time and act like they're best friends."
msgstr "Las personas en Kansai son muy amistosas. Puedes empezar una conversación con cualquiera en la calle, y te tratarán como si fueras un amigo de toda la vida."

msgctxt "2244_Erena"
msgid "But people around here always seem to act so formal, even around people who're their own age. It makes me a little nervous."
msgstr "En cambio, todos por aquí parecen actuar tan formal, incluso la gente de mi edad. Ver algo así me pone un poco nerviosa..."

msgctxt "2256_Akiyama"
msgid "I see. I hadn't thought of it that way."
msgstr "Entiendo eso, pero..."

msgctxt "2268_Akiyama"
msgid "Actually, I think I'm closer to the Kansai type. I've always thought of myself as laid-back."
msgstr "Sinceramente, me siento más como alguien de Kansai. Aunque pensándolo bien, siempre he creído que soy bastante relajado."

msgctxt "2280_Erena"
msgid "Maybe you're right."
msgstr "Je, je, je. ♪ \n"
"De seguro es tal y como dices. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2292_Erena"
msgid "I'm a little nervous around you, but that's because ya've got this aura about you."
msgstr "Aunque sea joven, tiene el aura de alguien grande. De alguna manera, me pone nerviosa, pero de forma positiva. ♪"

msgctxt "2304_Akiyama"
msgid "Uh-oh. I'm going to have to try and tone it down some more then. I'm pretty good at that."
msgstr "Ups, supongo que debo relajar un poco mi forma de hablar. Por suerte soy bueno en ello."

msgctxt "2316_Erena"
msgid "Ahahah! Ya don't have to go far. You're pretty funny."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! ♪\n"
"Tampoco es necesario que haga algo así. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>\n"
"Usted ya me parece alguien muy divertido. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2328_Akiyama"
msgid "You're not the shy type, are you?"
msgstr "Por lo visto te gusta hablar mucho."

msgctxt "2340_Erena"
msgid "Ahahah! That's for sure. If anything, I like to stand out!"
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja!\n"
"Eso es muy cierto.\n"
"Es que soy de las que les gusta llamar la atención. ♪"

msgctxt "2352_Akiyama"
msgid "I thought so. I could tell, even though we just met."
msgstr "Eso pensé. Me di cuenta de ello desde que te conocí."

msgctxt "2364_Erena"
msgid "In Kansai, you can just jump right in and start talkin' like you know someone, but that just seems to freak out people from Tokyo."
msgstr "En Kansai, puedes hablar de forma directa cualquier persona sin ningún problema, pero en Tokio pareciera que eso incomoda a muchas personas."

msgctxt "2376_Erena"
msgid "So I try to keep it under control at first."
msgstr "Por eso trato de mantenerme tranquilita cada que inicio una conversación..."

msgctxt "2388_Akiyama"
msgid "But you can't keep it up for long, can you?"
msgstr "Pero eventualmente, tu verdadera personalidad sale a la luz."

msgctxt "2400_Erena"
msgid "You saw right through me there."
msgstr "Ahaha. ♪\n"
"Por lo visto no puedo engañar a Akiyama-san. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2412_Akiyama"
msgid "You'll get used to it eventually. Don't be nervous."
msgstr "Ya te acostumbrarás. No te preocupes mucho por eso."

msgctxt "2424_Erena"
msgid "I'm glad you're so friendly."
msgstr "Je, je, je, me alegra que usted sea tan amigable. ♪"

msgctxt "2436_Erena"
msgid "I'm sure I'll feel more comfortable after we've had more time to talk."
msgstr "Estoy seguro de que, si seguimos conversando, usted terminará siendo todo un parlachín conmigo."

msgctxt "2448_Akiyama"
msgid "You mean you want me to request you?"
msgstr "¿Me estás pidiendo que te solicite?"

msgctxt "2460_Erena"
msgid "Hehe, yep!"
msgstr "¡Ajá! ♪\n"
"¿No quieres?"

msgctxt "2472_Akiyama"
msgid "Heheh. All right, I'll think about it."
msgstr "Je, je, je. Lo pensaré."

msgctxt "2484_Erena"
msgid "Welcome back!"
msgstr "Welcome back!"

msgctxt "2496_Akiyama"
msgid "How's it going? Have you gotten used to working here yet?"
msgstr "How's it going? Have you gotten used to working here yet?"

msgctxt "2508_Erena"
msgid "Thanks for thinkin' about me. You're sweet."
msgstr "Thanks for thinkin' about me. You're sweet."

msgctxt "2520_Erena"
msgid "I've gotten used to living here, but I have no sense of direction. I can never tell which train to take."
msgstr "I've gotten used to living here, but I have no sense of direction. I can never tell which train to take."

msgctxt "2532_Akiyama"
msgid "I see. Yeah, Kyoto is so neatly laid out compared to Tokyo. It must seem like total chaos to you."
msgstr "I see. Yeah, Kyoto is so neatly laid out compared to Tokyo. It must seem like total chaos to you."

msgctxt "2544_Erena"
msgid "Well, I'm trying to get used to it."
msgstr "Well, I'm trying to get used to it."

msgctxt "2556_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've\r\n"
"entered a club more than once. Please report this if you see this message."
msgstr "The dialogue will end after one round if you've\r\n"
"entered a club more than once. Please report this if you see this message."

msgctxt "2568_Erena"
msgid "Oh, Akiyama-san... You're not requesting me today?"
msgstr "Oh, Akiyama-san... ¿hoy no me vas a solicitar?"

msgctxt "2580_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, I, uh... I just thought I could use a little change of pace."
msgstr "Oh, I, uh... I just thought I could use a little change of pace."

msgctxt "2592_Erena"
msgid "Are you tired of me?"
